            </h3>
            <p class="text-blue-100 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">
              High-quality 3D models for products, prototypes and creative projects.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-8 border-t border-blue-700 mt-auto">
            <a href="/cad-modelling.html" class="block bg-white text-blue-600 font-bold uppercase text-center py-4 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-100 transition-colors">
